                .swiper-slide(style="background-image:url('images/main/slider-1.jpg');")
        
    .section-row.row-example
        
        p.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-duration="2s") ​Tenemos planes de <span>$5000 a $40.000</span> cuotas fijas de 3 a 12
        
